@DATABASE "E-Motion"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - E - E-Motion"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - E
                   ====================================

                                 E-Motion
                                 ========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40460,0)"}          40460,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35388,255)"}          35388,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
